						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone set up near Basavaṇṇa temple outside the village.</p>						

						<p>Jayakēśi II.</p>						

						<p>The inscription which refers to Vīra-Jayakēsi, is dated in the 12th regnal year, Virōdhi, Kārttika śu. 1 Thursday.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of Lahaḍa who was a <hi rend="italic">ḍiṁgariga</hi> servant of king Jayakēsi.</p>						

						</summary>
